Note that, although the above is explicitly tied to 4-dimensional spacetime,
 it can be generalized to aritrary Riemannian manifolds; see Jurgen Jost,
 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Riemannian Manifolds
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

